       agg-tot-ods-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione totale lordo righe ordine evase *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-agg-tot-ods-tle      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Start su file [ky2] per chiave #2               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
