      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Operazione di start                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           start     ky2    key not less
                            ky2-k01
                            invalid key
                            go to agg-tot-ods-600.
       agg-tot-ods-320.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura sequenziale [ky2]                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           read      ky2    next
                            with no lock
                            at end
                            go to agg-tot-ods-600.
