      *              * Test sul massimo                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        ky2-num-prt-1        not  = rf-oct-num-prt
                     go to agg-tot-ods-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Selezione sul record                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
