      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "CC"                 to   w-coe-cmb-vlt-ope      .
           move      rf-ocr-sgl-vpl       to   w-coe-cmb-vlt-sdv      .
           move      rf-ocr-tdc-vpl       to   w-coe-cmb-vlt-tdc      .
