           move      ky2-qta-dsp          to   w-det-imp-rig-qta      .
           move      rf-ocr-prz-net       to   w-det-imp-rig-prz      .
           move      rf-ocr-dec-prz       to   w-det-imp-rig-dep      .
           move      rf-ocr-sgl-vpp       to   w-det-imp-rig-svp      .
           move      rf-ocr-dec-vpp       to   w-det-imp-rig-dvp      .
           move      rf-ocr-tdc-vpp       to   w-det-imp-rig-tvp      .
           move      rf-ocr-cdc-vpp       to   w-det-imp-rig-cvp      .
           move      rf-oct-sgl-vpf       to   w-det-imp-rig-svf      .
           move      rf-oct-dec-vpf       to   w-det-imp-rig-dvf      .
           move      rf-oct-tdc-vpf       to   w-det-imp-rig-tvf      .
           move      rf-oct-cdc-vpf       to   w-det-imp-rig-cvf      .
           perform   det-imp-rig-000      thru det-imp-rig-999        .
           move      w-det-imp-rig-imp    to   ky2-imp-rig            .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
