      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Deviazione a seconda del tipo riga          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        ky2-tip-rig-tpr      =    "A"
                     go to agg-tot-ods-422
           else      go to agg-tot-ods-424.
       agg-tot-ods-422.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
